id: pm-qrxb
title: "SDK docs: document cli-contracts exports and extension capability requirements"
description: "SDK audit found gaps: (1) docs/SDK.md does not document the large cli-contracts layer (PM_CORE_COMMAND_NAMES, PM_TOOL_ACTIONS, PM_TOOL_PARAMETERS_SCHEMA, flag contracts). (2) docs/EXTENSIONS.md does not note that registerCommand with inline flags requires schema capability, and registerExporter requires importers capability."
